===== FOR CHANGING TEXTURING AND COCKPIT LETTERING FONTS =====
To get the lettering fonts (futura) and changes for the cockpit, download everything in the Cockpit folder of this repo and paste it to 
the Cockpit folder of the 777VMD. 

===== FOR CHANGING CDU, PFD, EICAS STUFFS =====
To get the renewed CDU and PFD fonts, download all the fonts in the fonts folder in the github, and then paste it all to the 
fonts folder of the 777VMD. After placing the fonts, download the entire cdu stuffs in this github and passte it to the cdu folder of the 
777VMD, and yeah, do the same process for the PFD and EICAS as well. 
